## Quick Decision Matrix

| Context | Has Buttons in Row? | Badge Style |
|---------|-------------------|-------------|
| Table row | ✅ Yes | `badgeStyle="outlined"` |
| Table row | ❌ No | `badgeStyle="filled"` or default |
| Stat card | N/A | `badgeStyle="filled"` or default |
| Alert banner | N/A | `badgeStyle="filled"` or default |
| Header section | N/A | `badgeStyle="filled"` or default |
| Modal content | Depends | Use filled unless buttons compete visually |

## Implementation Checklist

When creating or reviewing table components with status indicators:

- [ ] Does the table row contain action buttons?
- [ ] Does the table row contain status badges?
- [ ] If both: Are badges using `badgeStyle="outlined"`?
- [ ] Are helper functions (like `getStatusBadge`) configured to return outlined badges?
- [ ] Do standalone badge contexts (cards, headers) still use filled badges appropriately?

